{"tid":561388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警否認非法性交 今獲准候審期間離港外遊10天","createTime":"2018-02-15T03:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T09:20:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e8805f8474dbcb1acd87a90478fd7ec365e90d3a","tid":561388,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180215/large/1518664405_7e48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180215%2Flarge%2F1518664405_7e48.jpg&h=e110eac6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警員涉嫌於2013年1月至10月期間，於屯門區與一名當時15歲的女童性交，早前被控與年齡在16歲以下的女童非法性交罪，他今在屯門裁判法院否認控罪，裁判官將案排期至4月17日審理。<br />\n<br />\n控方透露將有5名控方證人出庭，並申請事主可於屏風後作供及使用特別通道進出法庭，裁判官批准申請。<br />\n<br />\n被告陳健敏（38歲）可繼續保釋並不得干擾控方證人。辯方則指因已報旅行團外遊，申請候審期間有10天離港，在控方不反對下，裁判官批准申請但將保釋金由2,000元提高至5,000元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180215/57836153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180215%2F57836153&d=f9NUqfofeIko5MxKqjpakGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=f96be8c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180215%2F57836153&h=4d05d1f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180215/57836153</a>"},{"pid":"05d5fdc3945c7b0305dea9cac2f87c52b92021ef","tid":561388,"uid":128565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:28:35.000Z","msg":"我強調警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"0ce6d9a56c1d0a00c676ae3c63db07cba10ef906","tid":561388,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"05d5fdc3945c7b0305dea9cac2f87c52b92021ef","tid":561388,"uid":128565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:28:35.000Z","msg":"我強調警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理